      <p>Made with &lt;3 by ðŸ¤–.</p>
      <p>Nothing on this site is supposed to be construed as medical advice.  Talk to your doctor about those topics.</p>
      <p>JDRF does not sponsor, authorize, or endorse any of the content on this website.</p>
      </footer>
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.1.1.min.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/semantic-ui@2.4.2/dist/semantic.min.js"></script>
    <script src="/js/guess.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
